Why Expense Tracker?
--------------------

1. Add purchase items
2. Visualize expenditures


Install
-------

1. Checkout the source
2. Put in your web server's publicly accessible html directory
** Note: ** You will need latest versions of LAMP or WAMP installed.


How to use
----------

1. Point you browser to the URL where you installed the Expense Tracker
2. Begin adding you purchases

Author
------
Artyom Gordiyevsky is a good person with a hackeristic attitude to life.


